==Drops==
{{DropLogProject|kills=60120}}

The listed quantities are for soloing Venenatis. In group encounters, Venenatis's drops, including uniques, will be split proportionally based on damage done. Up to 10 players may obtain drops per kill in this manner, and each of the top 10 players will receive at least 25% of the solo loot quantity.

Ironmen must deal 7% of the overall damage to be eligible for 25% of the solo loot quantity. Ironmen dealing less than 7% damage will receive a minimum of 5% of the solo loot quantity.

The average solo Venenatis kill is worth {{Coins|{{Average drop value|mob=Venenatis|mobname=solo Venenatis|raw=yes}}}}. This increases marginally to {{Coins|{{Average drop value|mob=Venenatis|brimstone=yes|raw=yes}}}} on a [[Konar quo Maten|Konar]] task, or {{Coins|{{Average drop value|mob=Venenatis|wildernessslayer=yes|raw=yes}}}} on a [[Krystilia]] task.

