==Trivia==
* Venenatis' 2014 model was a recoloured version of [[Kalrag]].
* She was a player-suggested [[boss]], which was adopted into the game after a substantial amount of positive forum feedback.
* The term Venenatis comes from the Latin "[[wiktionary:venenatis|venēnātīs]]", which means "venomous" or "poisoned".
* Despite her name's origin and Phabelle Bile mentioning Venenatis does indeed produce venom, she and her spiderlings are not [[venom|venomous]] or [[poisonous]] to players. This is leftover from before the Wilderness boss rework, when her attacks inflicted poison.
* If someone starts a battle with Venenatis, but leaves the cave without killing her, she will de-spawn after 10 minutes.

